So in the past, the menu colour would more or less match an open window frame colour.<br />With the suggested new settings, the menu and taskbar match instead. <br />I installed new version and adjusted to your Win 8 skin values.<br />Does match nicely when changing desktop background with auto colour task bar enabled.<br />I tried tweaking myself, but difficult with a cheap LCD twistflex monitor, with viewing angle errors,<br />so I'm sticking to GauravK's settings.<br /><br />Excellent feature:)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> â€” Sat Aug 31, 2013 3:10 pm</p><hr />
